			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S325">Mr. Udall of Colorado</sponsor>
			 (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S330">Mr. Bennet</cosponsor>) introduced
			 the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the
			 <committee-name committee-id="SSEG00">Committee on Energy and Natural
			 Resources</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
