              <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/16/2104">16 U.S.C. 2104</external-xref> note</cato:entity-ref>; <cato:entity-ref entity-type="public-law" value="public-law/105/277">Public Law
			 105–277</cato:entity-ref>)</cato:entity> is repealed.</text>
			</subsection>
    </section>
